text: REAL BAD CUSTOMER SERVICES. HOW COULD THEY ASKED CUSTOMERS TO WAIT OUTSIDE?! is it a rule ? if not why need to do such a thing

A well run local styled bakery offering a range of snacks, breads, cakes and pastries that Singaporeans love.

Though small in size this branch has one the best service anywhere. Casher is courteous and multilingual.

Glad to have found this place, a gem in provincial Teban.
Friendly staff. I always go there to buy the pizza bread
Cheap n good variety of Bun selections despite small outlet.
